rows.label: tev910701_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910701_SEL0020
rows.name: Ask him about Smile Pizza.

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0030
rows.name:
Grins all around—Smile Pizza Kitchen!
Pies by the pound—Smile Pizza Kitchen![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0040
rows.name:
Double the toppings? Hey bud, no sweat!
Loyalty discounts? C'mon now, you bet!!![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0050
rows.name: Phew... What am I doing with my life...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_JNK0060
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910701_SEL0070
rows.name: Ask how he's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0080
rows.name:
My old man's a big-wig at one of
the arms manufacturers, and he's
mean like the devil himself...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0090
rows.name:
Do you know, he kicked me outta the
residential district! Yeah, like that was
gonna make me "contribute to society"...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0100
rows.name:
Well, for the time being, I'm working at
Smile Pizza for minimum wage plus tips...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0110
rows.name:
Jeeeeez, I wish I had it in me
to be a BLADE...![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_JNK0120
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910701_SEL0130
rows.name: Ask about Smile Pizza's business prospects.

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0140
rows.name:
Oh, you won't believe how many Ma-non
customers we get these days. We're
selling pies faster than we can make 'em.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0150
rows.name:
Though to be fair, we sell less
than Army Pizza sells...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0160
rows.name:
Every time I look in, they're running
around like there's a five-alarm fire.
Those guys must be making bank![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_JNK0170
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910701_SEL0180
rows.name: Ask how he's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0190
rows.name:
The Ma-non like to come in and order
a whole stack of pizzas in one go.
Honestly, I wish they didn't.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0200
rows.name:
Every time, they clear us out of toppings.
It's not like we can just get more from
a supermarket.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0210
rows.name:
*sigh* Guess it's time to get the
Mediators on the provisioning job again...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_JNK0220
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910701_SEL0230
rows.name: Ask about Al.

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0240
rows.name:
First time I saw him, his vibe was totally
different. I didn't recognize him at all...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0250
rows.name:
Like, what, you're telling me that super
intense dude was THE Alois Bernholt,
the hero who saved the White Whale...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0260
rows.name:
Man... If I'd known, I could've
asked for an autograph...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_JNK0270
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910701_SEL0280
rows.name: Ask how he's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0290
rows.name:
That cool dude that was here earlier—he
made something click into place for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0300
rows.name:
If I've got time to be mouthing off about
my old man, I might as well bake an extra
pie and send it to him...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0310
rows.name:
I've actually started feeling some pride
in my work lately. The manager even gave
me a raise—still in disbelief about that...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0320
rows.name:
Anyway, my point is, I don't wanna live
my life mired in regrets. From now on,
I'm cutting back on the looking back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0330
rows.name: Cancel

rows.label: tev910701_MSG0340
rows.name: Cancel
